snippet.title: Friend Sighting Trailer - Showfest 2019
snippet.description:
The trailer for the up and coming game Friend Sighting! Play as Mothman at a college for cryptids, making friends and flying around while keeping your student loans down. 

Interested in this game? Follow Friend Sighting on twitter at @FriendSighting!

This trailer was produced for WPI's Showfest 2019.
